I have 20 minutes to talk
about three billion years

00:13:50.490 --> 00:13:51.660
worth of Earth history.

00:13:51.660 --> 00:13:56.790
So I think the reason
that rust features

00:13:56.790 --> 00:14:00.770
prominently in my title will
become apparent during my talk.

