01:02:40.600 --> 01:02:42.220
is a microbial process.

01:02:42.220 --> 01:02:47.040
Most of the methane we
see in natural iron seeps

01:02:47.040 --> 01:02:48.670
is coming from methanogens.

01:02:48.670 --> 01:02:52.110
That was presumably a very
ancient group of organisms.

01:02:52.110 --> 01:02:53.730
I mean, they're very
