01:02:57.410 --> 01:03:00.900
So that development of
methanogenesis and the methane

01:03:00.900 --> 01:03:06.090
production was certainly-- I
mean that might alone, as well

01:03:06.090 --> 01:03:10.177
as-- well, and then
also CO2 fixation,

01:03:10.177 --> 01:03:11.510
which we also didn't talk about.

01:03:11.510 --> 01:03:14.020
The other major innovation
besides photosynthesis

01:03:14.020 --> 01:03:17.260
