meteorites hitting the Earth.

01:05:09.250 --> 01:05:12.520
But there's also accumulating
evidence that a lot of it

01:05:12.520 --> 01:05:16.540
just came from rock
reactions, condensation

01:05:16.540 --> 01:05:20.210
as the planet condensed to
become a hard, rocky planet,

01:05:20.210 --> 01:05:22.870
that water was released
from those reactions, too.

